<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.9.6">
<l>nēcami lātavark kumniṉai yātavark kumariyāṉ</l>
<l>vācama larppoḻil cūḻvaṭa māmatu raippiṟantāṉ</l>
<l>tēcamel lāmvaṇaṅ kumtiru māliruñ cōlainiṉṟa</l>
<l>kēcava nampitaṉ ṉaikkeṇṭai yoṇkaṇṇi kāṇuṅkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will the girl with bright, carp eyes look on Prince Keśava</l>
<l>Who stands in Tirumāliruñcōlai where all the lands worship,</l>
<l>The one who was born in the great northern Mathurā,</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by groves of scented flowers,</l>
<l>The one who is difficult for those without devotion</l>
<l rend="indent">and for those who do not believe?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
